---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'About';
const description = 'About Andrew the Coder';
const permalink = `${Astro.site.href}about`;
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} permalink={permalink} current="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <figure class="about-image">
      <img src="/assets/about-illustration.webp" alt="Illustration of a notebook" width="330">
      <figcaption>
        Illustration by
        <a href="https://icons8.com/illustrations/author/5c07e68d82bcbc0092519bb6" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Icons 8</a>
        from
        <a href="https://icons8.com/illustrations" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ouch!</a>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
    <p>Hi, I'm Andrew, a software engineer and web developer with over 20 years of experience. I've had the opportunity to work with a diverse range of languages, frameworks, and platforms throughout my career. I thrive on the problem-solving aspects of software development and am always eager to tackle new challenges.</p>
    <p>Beyond coding, I hold advanced degrees in theology and linguistics, which have broadened my perspective and analytical skills. My major hobby is music, and I'm an avid guitar player.</p>

    <h2>Languages I work with:</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>JavaScript</li>
      <li>PHP</li>
      <li>Golang</li>
      <li>OCaml</li>
      <li>Rust</li>
      <li>Zig</li>
      <li>C/C++</li>
      <li>Python</li>
      <li>Ruby</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Frameworks I'm familiar with:</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Symfony</li>
      <li>Laravel</li>
      <li>Flask</li>
      <li>Django</li>
      <li>Rails</li>
      <li>Spring Boot</li>
      <li>Gin</li>
      <li>Leptos</li>
      <li>Rocket</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-image {
    display: block;
    margin: 2em auto; /* Center the image and add vertical margin */
    max-width: 300px;
    text-align: center; /* Center the caption */
  }

  .about-image img {
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }

  .about-image figcaption {
    font-size: 0.8em;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 2em; /* Add more space above h2s */
    margin-bottom: 0.8em;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: disc; /* Ensure list style is visible */
    padding-left: 1.5em;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5em;
  }
</style>
